nderstanding low level stuff how programming is done like how physical switch like 0,1 done and how c works, its basically you are trying to make fool out of students. I personally actually reverse engineer so many software extensions their meta data everything so your ai thing is not even close to reality, ai use its weight to give output cos ai dont want to look stupid, so basically you are ruining someone’s life based on something you dont even know or understand its concepts.", "timestamp": 1775581147}, {"author": "matutuxa", "author_id": "3264817277", "id": "18050630771532130", "text": "So you are using AI to check if your students used AI. You are not serious", "timestamp": 1775579768}, {"author": "__vicsparklez", "author_id": "55454630", "id": "18125100394595406", "text": "Wtf", "timestamp": 1775571246}, {"author": "iam.potato.czar", "author_id": "67594654839", "id": "17884674405378033", "text": "Well I have bad news for you ma’am. IA can simulate whatever you need. Not a problem at all.", "timestamp": 1775567577}, {"author": "aurnob_censored", "author_id": "57988740041", "id": "17992762739945908", "text": "😂 already learned how to counter that😂. We don't fail we learn.", "timestamp": 1775567514}, {"author": "caw_555", "author_id": "31474818350", "id": "18576339511043840", "text": "So do it in chat GPT and then simply type it out and you will pass but ones who copy paste exactly the same text fail! That doesn’t sound right to me !", "timestamp": 1775564148}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/656585743_1647477263268956_3367609833329439442_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4Lm5mcmFtZV9jb3Zlcl9mcmFtZS5jMiJ9&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=108&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gHY4S0iEuhM59znAnPWw25I1Eje26j-per7nWTSWBBfkRYs_4JnRtkkioCAIRlFPVc&_nc_ohc=6gNCQ1DcXyYQ7kNvwG5DJuw&_nc_gid=v6vcxvyt2-UXtPc8bpPUog&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af0P4OLF2CEk4fwA8L-v_Otiq8aPgy